@startuml
autonumber

actor "Usuário" as U
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "AuthService" as AS
participant "PrismaService" as DB

== Registro ==
U -> FE : Preenche cadastro
FE -> AC : POST /auth/register
AC -> AS : register(dto)
AS -> DB : Cria Usuario
DB --> AS : Usuario criado
AS --> AC : Resultado
AC --> FE : 201 Created

== Login ==
U -> FE : Informa email e senha
FE -> AC : POST /auth/login
AC -> AS : login(dto)
AS -> DB : Busca usuário + valida senha
DB --> AS : Usuário válido
AS --> AC : accessToken + refreshToken
AC --> FE : 200 + accessToken\nSet-Cookie(refreshToken)

== Refresh ==
FE -> AC : POST /auth/refresh\n(cookie refreshToken)
AC -> AS : refresh(refreshToken)
AS -> DB : Valida refresh token persistido
DB --> AS : Token válido
AS --> AC : Novo accessToken
AC --> FE : 200 + accessToken

== Perfil ==
FE -> AC : GET /auth/me\n(Bearer accessToken)
AC --> FE : 200 + dados do usuário

== Esqueci senha ==
U -> FE : Solicita redefinição de senha
FE -> AC : POST /auth/forgot-password
AC -> AS : forgotPassword(email)
AS --> AC : Instruções/token de redefinição
AC --> FE : 200 OK

== Redefinir senha ==
U -> FE : Informa token e nova senha
FE -> AC : POST /auth/reset-password
AC -> AS : resetPassword(dto)
AS -> DB : Atualiza hash da senha
DB --> AS : OK
AS --> AC : Senha redefinida
AC --> FE : 200 OK

== Excluir conta ==
U -> FE : Solicita exclusão da conta
FE -> AC : POST /api/auth/delete\n(Bearer accessToken)
AC -> AS : deleteAccount(userId)
AS -> DB : Remove usuário e dados associados
DB --> AS : OK
AS --> AC : Conta excluída
AC --> FE : 200 OK

== Logout ==
FE -> AC : POST /auth/logout
AC -> AS : logout(refreshToken)
AS -> DB : Limpa refresh token
DB --> AS : OK
AC --> FE : 200 + clear cookie
@enduml
